=== EXAMPLE: scdoc_Guides_Multichannel-Expansion_ex19 ===

DESCRIPTION: A neutral pure_tone sound, with complex oscillator character around 100 Hz, featuring punchy attack and compressed envelope, with evolving spectral movement, and filtered with resonant_steep_rolloff character.

CATEGORIES:
  attack_time: punchy
  brightness: neutral
  crest_factor_db: compressed
  envelope_flatness: flat
  harmonic_to_noise_ratio: pure_tone
  spectral_complexity_mean: moderate
  spectral_flux_normalized: evolving
  spectral_slope: steep_rolloff
  temporal_centroid: balanced

SYNTHESIS CONCEPTS (key values):
[oscillator]
  fundamental_freq: 100.0000
  harmonic_decay_rate: 13.6952
  harmonic_regularity: 0.6937
  pitch_clarity: 378.9508
  inharmonicity: 0.0000
  type: complex
[filter]
  spectral_slope: -23.0309
  resonance_freq: 559.8633

SUPERCOLLIDER CODE:
